{"type": "article", "id": 27473, "title": "儿童节，给有童心的人一份礼物吧丨这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-05-28T07:04:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 918, "name": "儿童节"}, {"id": 5504, "name": "礼物"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 367, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702160034XM6SBn9KQ8RTfl7D.jpeg", "contents": "\r\n\r\n<p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p>你还会每年过儿童节吗，如果家里有小朋友，这也是一年中最忙碌的时刻吧。想想当初总是因为要上台表演而紧张，因为可以多放半天假而期待，但现在即便没有隆重的活动，也能成为同学聚会的理由呢。我们挑选了一些儿童节的礼物，如果没有送礼的人选，就请送给自己并说一声“儿童节快乐”。</p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<h2>LUC – EXQUISITE CORPSE by Mathieu Lang</h2>\r\n<p>这面像挂钟一样的圆盘可以玩图画接龙，外面一层彩色圆盘有一个缺口，也将下面垫上的白纸分成了六的部分，它需要 6 个人在不同的空白处画出很有故事性的图案，画的过程中，每个人都无法看到其他人的图画，最后打开后就形成一个有趣的连环故事。设计者来自瑞典的设计师 <a href=\"http://mathieulang.ch/portfolio/luc-exquisite-corpse/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mathieu Lang</a> ，这个设计在今年爱马仕以“玩”为主题的 Prix Emile Hermès 比赛中获胜。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160003TO9SVUez6cBFJtuA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021600044OjSe5kyDsZ2tzUq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160005NWRhm4JlQdM0oibO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160005srZu7IEKwa9e3Nd5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160006oplLgFOIkU3V2jad.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Boss By Jaime Hayón</h2>\r\n<p class=\"\">西班牙设计师 Jaime Hayón 的陶瓷作品常常带有一份童真，他和意大利著名陶瓷品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bosatrade.com/en/Collections#filter=*\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bosa Ceramiche</a> 合作设计了不少经典款，比如 Strypy 花瓶，用点和线条勾勒出具有几何感的图案，点缀一些彩色的圆点，模拟了儿童天真的画笔又具有装饰性。还有动物面罩、希望鸟等，金色点缀其中显得典雅而不俗气。<br></p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160007Zs9NDUK3b80rAWCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160007pyrtCbYmZSgs2Xxq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160008wpF4kPW0b8KTId5R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160009q2h3dEKALbjylrxN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160010Sxv4dK3jyi7HheRW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>PHYSIC CIRCUS by Alexandre Echasseriau</h2>\r\n<p>法国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.alexandreechasseriau.com/PHYSICS-CIRCUS\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexandre Echasseriau</a> 与物理学家一起合作了这款物理马戏团（PHYSIC CIRCUS），需要按照模板拼出两只立体小鸟的形状，其中小鸟的身体需要粘水使之弯曲。小鸟和正下面的木板内含有同极磁铁，洒上液氮降温后再加上超导的通电线圈，可以让小鸟悬浮起来，就像一场物理实验。有趣的是，“舞台”“灯光”和各种道具都装在一个可随身携带的木盒子里，就像送出了一场有趣的表演。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160010T0sGNpf8aiRho5M7.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51641791\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160011nrpq5Ekv74SR39Pg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160011wUN41tqYKPaAip97.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160012sMy57TGmN2DPkn1B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160013tSjrfXixv4G6JABC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160014B3rJgCj1RSOLUo9Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<h2>Nomad Travel Blanket by EllieFunDay</h2>\r\n<p>虽然不是童话故事中会飞的魔毯，EllieFunDay 推出的这款名为 Nomad 的旅行毯依然可以成为小朋友们可靠的旅伴。它采用 100% 有机棉织成，有三种不同的动物造型并且取上了冒险家的名字（比如大熊猫就叫马可）。摊开的时候它是一条毯子，折叠后可以变成一只小背包，也可以作为小抱枕使用。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-nomad-travel-blanket-from-ellie-fun-day#/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 68 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160015EGFi2sVuCg5URbZO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.02555366\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160015WpdCwBVDb9hGncPj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57866184\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160016IHl9cjBTv0zyuMhf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160016h2i5Ze1AONdaxHKr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3650519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>ISSA mikro by Foreo</h2>\r\n<p>刷牙这件事对年纪较小的孩子和父母来说都是一项考验，Foreo 为此专门设计了这款 ISSA mikro 牙刷，适合 0 到 4 岁的孩子使用。牙刷的刷毛由柔软的硅橡胶制成，配合声波震动的刷牙方式能够减少对牙龈的刺激，减轻孩子对刷牙的抗拒心理。使用时牙刷柄上还会亮起一张笑脸，以便分散孩子的注意力。如果你对这款牙刷感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/issa-mikro-revolutionary-baby-electric-toothbrush#/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 79 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160017b2DijCcEvq8KAp6w.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09032258\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160017eRuZ4xmgjwAcFSIh.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48064516\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160018mb4sNz8gD1PCQIiZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99676375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160019oFMDvEScU8Hyr4h9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59747292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<h2>Herd of Mini Robot Horses by Monroe Workshop</h2>\r\n<p>会说话的小熊、吞象的蛇……孩子们的小脑袋中总是充满了各种有趣甚至有些疯狂的想法，一份奇奇怪怪的玩具可以鼓励他们的创造力。<a href=\"http://www.monroeworkshop.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Monroe Workshop</a> 推出的小马机器人有着圆圆的眼睛和方方正正的身体，看上去不仅可爱，硬木和棉绳的结合还透露出一种温暖的感觉。这是它的购买<a href=\"http://www.monroeworkshop.com/collections/toys/products/herd-of-mini-horses\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>，两只的价格为 25 美元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160020wyhFvtCo8urP5ifH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160020M7LZdOlK3Rb2Nn9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160021hqviU1BM4w23xYOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160022CEJa6vPoWbkAHQ05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160022mXMF96pVCRlyGsSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Elephant by Hyunsoo Choi, Taego Yoon</h2>\r\n<p>动物玩偶的确是个很保险的点子，但更让孩子们惊喜的或许是一款专门为他们设计的动物造型的家具，比如这个由韩国设计师 Hyunsoo Choi 和 Taego Yoon 共同打造的大象桌椅。它的椅背就像是一张小象的脸，黄色的坐垫可以穿过小孔变成一个短短的象鼻同时也起到了固定坐垫的作用。桌椅两侧专门设计了弧形的凹槽，便于搬运。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021600239XsaZpSQPRzcLf7m.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160023z1iCUfN83JHPvqOd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160024Me32KPtG7H80n1XF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160025JaWkXLbRYNdp69fi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>LeeLuu by LeeLuu Labs</h2>\r\n<p>夜幕降临，小朋友们有时会被自己想象中的怪兽给吓到，而一个依靠拥抱作为能量的玩偶夜灯可以陪伴他们度过漫漫长夜。这款名为 LeeLuu 的夜灯由四位来自芬兰的女设计师共同研发，一旦搂紧它就会散发出温柔的光芒，通过抚摸它的光线则会慢慢变暗，最后又变回普通玩偶的模样。可爱的动物造型搭配讨巧的感应式设计，会成为孩子们的好伙伴。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/leeluu-the-magical-touch-sensitive-nightlight--2#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 79 欧元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160026ITZ9i8GfgWoEcASD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160030EhmBvaWO3fDp6V2i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63870968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021600319WtSkRU3YVlp52NC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73225806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160032VUe18BiAdS7O0Hvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56290323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160032KNrXCT9qbAYcikFR.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52916667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n"}